px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">4.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 华文仿宋;\">《长沙市哲学社会科学规划项目管理办法》</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, 宋体, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: right; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 33px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, 宋体, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: right; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 33px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 华文仿宋; text-align: left;\">科技处</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; text-align: left;\">/</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 华文仿宋; text-align: left;\">学科建设办公室</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, 宋体, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: right; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 33px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; text-align: left;\">2018</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 华文仿宋; text-align: left;\">年</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; text-align: left;\">2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 华文仿宋; text-align: left;\">月</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px